  <h4 class="collectionName">
    <a href="/opinion/zh-hant" target="_blank">
      觀點與評論 • <span>OPINION</span>
    </a>
  </h4>
	<ul class="commentSummaryList" data-tb-region="comment-piece-comment-big-byline-0">
		<li class="commentSummaryItem  first " data-tb-region-item> <h3 class="commentSummaryHeadline"><a target="_blank" href="/opinion/20250926/asia-protest-youth-nepal-bangladesh/zh-hant/" title="青年的吶喊：抗議之聲點燃「亞洲之春」">青年的吶喊：抗議之聲點燃「亞洲之春」</a></h3>
<h6 class="byline"> <span class="en_byline">MEENA KANDASAMY</span> </h6>
<div class="thumbnail">
	<a href="/opinion/20250926/asia-protest-youth-nepal-bangladesh/zh-hant/" title="青年的吶喊：抗議之聲點燃「亞洲之春」">
		<img src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/09/21/multimedia/19kandasamy-gqtv/19kandasamy-gqtv-thumbLarge-v4.jpg" alt="" width="50" height="50"/>
	</a>
</div>

<p class="summary">十多年前，Twitter推動了阿拉伯之春；如今，同樣由年輕人發起的反抗運動在亞洲重現。掌權者若視而不見，將為此付出代價。</p>
 </li>
		<li class="commentSummaryItem  " data-tb-region-item> <h3 class="commentSummaryHeadline"><a target="_blank" href="/opinion/20250925/china-tech-climate/zh-hant/" title="中國告別綠色「內卷」是福是禍？">中國告別綠色「內卷」是福是禍？</a></h3>
<h6 class="byline"> <span class="en_byline">DAVID WALLACE-WELLS</span> </h6>
<div class="thumbnail">
	<a href="/opinion/20250925/china-tech-climate/zh-hant/" title="中國告別綠色「內卷」是福是禍？">
		<img src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/09/25/opinion/25wallace-wells-newsletter-image/25wallace-wells-newsletter-image-thumbLarge.jpg" alt="" width="50" height="50"/>
	</a>
</div>

<p class="summary">北京也許不會突然關閉綠色製造和可再生能源出口的閥門，但習近平已經宣稱他希望結束內卷，開啟一個不以低價競爭為核心的新產業戰略。</p>
 </li>
		<li class="commentSummaryItem  last " data-tb-region-item> <h3 class="commentSummaryHeadline"><a target="_blank" href="/opinion/20250924/china-economy-deflation-neijuan/zh-hant/" title="令中國感到恐懼的一個新聞熱詞">令中國感到恐懼的一個新聞熱詞</a></h3>
<h6 class="byline"> <span class="en_byline">BOB DAVIS</span> </h6>
<div class="thumbnail">
	<a href="/opinion/20250924/china-economy-deflation-neijuan/zh-hant/" title="令中國感到恐懼的一個新聞熱詞">
		<img src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/09/23/opinion/23Davis/23Davis-thumbLarge.jpg" alt="" width="50" height="50"/>
	</a>
</div>

<p class="summary">中國正在走向通貨緊縮，領導人將這一問題歸咎於「內卷」，並試圖通過行政手段來遏制這一現象。但這些措施難以從根本上解決問題。</p>
 </li>
	</ul>
</div>
<div class="commentHeadlineOnly  last ">
	 
